mork
Enum EventType

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<EventType>
      mork.EventType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<EventType>
public enum EventType
extends Enum<EventType>

The MorkParser fires events and each event has a type EventType and an optional String value. This enumeration represents all possible event types which can occur while parsing a Mork database file.

Author:
mhaller
